  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/4f8ade20f600cdb5eca97dca1a83f0c6.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/4f8ade20f600cdb5eca97dca1a83f0c6.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/4f8ade20f600cdb5eca97dca1a83f0c6.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BROKEN MIND is an action Survival Horror. Investigate, solve the puzzles and find out what happened to Laura Campbell. If she is still alive you must act quickly!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT HAPPENED TO LAURA CAMPBELL?</h2><br>In BROKEN MIND, you play Agent Frank Morgan, a detective with a dark past. You will have to investigate the disappearance of a teenage girl who was abducted during a live Internet broadcast. The investigation is accelerated when Laura's phone emits a signal a few miles away in the middle of the forest!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE</h2><br>BROKEN MIND is a narrative game that requires you to fight. In the course of your investigation, you'll encounter numerous enemies who will try to stand in your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/a0b3b61e011a0882d1ba86a154953054.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/a0b3b61e011a0882d1ba86a154953054.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/a0b3b61e011a0882d1ba86a154953054.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SOLVE PUZZLES</h2><br>During your investigation, you'll come across a number of puzzles that you'll need to solve. Keep a close eye on your surroundings for clues.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/eb22ad7ea39a1a6fbbcdb5679e43e9a4.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/eb22ad7ea39a1a6fbbcdb5679e43e9a4.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/eb22ad7ea39a1a6fbbcdb5679e43e9a4.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOU'LL HAVE TO BE DISCRET</h2><br>Sometimes fighting isn't an option, so you'll have to hide to avoid being caught by your assailants.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/6f347613487e55d3946a216490d3591f.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/6f347613487e55d3946a216490d3591f.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/6f347613487e55d3946a216490d3591f.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNIQUE HAND MADE DRAWINGS</h2><br>Discover a dark, oppressive atmosphere with graphics that blend 3D scenery and hand-drawn images.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/d6d9556f6026aebad295095bc185bdd2.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/d6d9556f6026aebad295095bc185bdd2.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/d6d9556f6026aebad295095bc185bdd2.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>- A narrative game with gameplay that mixes investigations, puzzles and combat!<br>- Follow the story from different angles, playing several characters with unique skills.<br>- Fully voice acted game thanks to 7 actors.<br>- An oppressive atmosphere, with a graphic style mixing 3D and hand made drawings<br>- The biggest project of the studio !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/54f23a760ff04faba486b5fec1df7692.avif?t=1721306330\" width=608 height=338 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/4f8ade20f600cdb5eca97dca1a83f0c6.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/4f8ade20f600cdb5eca97dca1a83f0c6.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/4f8ade20f600cdb5eca97dca1a83f0c6.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BROKEN MIND is an action Survival Horror. Investigate, solve the puzzles and find out what happened to Laura Campbell. If she is still alive you must act quickly!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHAT HAPPENED TO LAURA CAMPBELL?</h2><br>In BROKEN MIND, you play Agent Frank Morgan, a detective with a dark past. You will have to investigate the disappearance of a teenage girl who was abducted during a live Internet broadcast. The investigation is accelerated when Laura's phone emits a signal a few miles away in the middle of the forest!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE</h2><br>BROKEN MIND is a narrative game that requires you to fight. In the course of your investigation, you'll encounter numerous enemies who will try to stand in your way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/a0b3b61e011a0882d1ba86a154953054.poster.avif?t=1721306330\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/a0b3b61e011a0882d1ba86a154953054.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/a0b3b61e011a0882d1ba86a154953054.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4