06330\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/d6d9556f6026aebad295095bc185bdd2.webm?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/d6d9556f6026aebad295095bc185bdd2.mp4?t=1721306330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><br>- A narrative game with gameplay that mixes investigations, puzzles and combat!<br>- Follow the story from different angles, playing several characters with unique skills.<br>- Fully voice acted game thanks to 7 actors.<br>- An oppressive atmosphere, with a graphic style mixing 3D and hand made drawings<br>- The biggest project of the studio !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2559950/extras/54f23a760ff04faba486b5fec1df7692.avif?t=1721306330\" width=608 height=338 /></span>",
